<dec f='Modules/Image/Contrib/TurboJpeg/turbojpeg.h' l='976' type='int tjPlaneWidth(int componentID, int width, int subsamp)'/>
<doc f='Modules/Image/Contrib/TurboJpeg/turbojpeg.h' l='962'>/**
 * The plane width of a YUV image plane with the given parameters.  Refer to
 * @ref YUVnotes &quot;YUV Image Format Notes&quot; for a description of plane width.
 *
 * @param componentID ID number of the image plane (0 = Y, 1 = U/Cb, 2 = V/Cr)
 *
 * @param width width (in pixels) of the YUV image
 *
 * @param subsamp level of chrominance subsampling in the image (see
 * @ref TJSAMP &quot;Chrominance subsampling options&quot;.)
 *
 * @return the plane width of a YUV image plane with the given parameters, or
 * -1 if the arguments are out of bounds.
 */</doc>
